             was indicted for <rs id="t18230409-71-off383" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18230409-71-off383" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18230409-71-off383" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18230409-71-cd384" type="crimeDate">31st of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230409-71-off383 t18230409-71-cd384"></join>, a looking glass, value 20 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18230409-71-victim720" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Davis
                  <interp inst="t18230409-71-victim720" type="surname" value="Davis"></interp>
